# Implementation

**Server-first** — `"use client"` only when needed.

**Suspense:** only slices that use request APIs (`cookies`, `headers`, `connection`, …). Static / `'use cache'` shells stay **outside** Suspense.

**Session:** `auth-session.ts` only — request-scoped `cache()`; never `use cache` / revalidate session. Dashboard tree: `requireAuthSession()` without `redirectTo` under `dashboard/layout`.

**Actions:** `src/app/action/<feature>/` — one mutation per file. Cache invalidation: `caching.mdc` / [caching.md](docs/agents/caching.md).

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/implementation.md](docs/agents/implementation.md) — session table, Suspense examples, definition of done. **UI styling:** [ui-design.md](docs/agents/ui-design.md). **Nav copy:** [dashboard.md](docs/agents/dashboard.md).
